headline: A First Take On CG Oncology
summary: CG Oncology's stock has dropped 40% since its IPO peak, driven by profit-taking and competitive concerns despite promising Phase 3 data for Cretostimogene. Learn more on CGON stock here.

headline: High Expectations And Data Disappointments Have Driven Daiichi Sankyo Lower
summary: Daiichi Sankyo's stock dropped 25% due to disappointing clinical data, but upcoming studies could drive a rebound for risk-tolerant investors. See more here.
